README
- describes how to start vftpd as a docker container and other things
  related to building the docker container

docker-vsftpd
- docker related files and things for building and running the vftpd
  docker container

ReplayServerApp
- probably the directory you want, contains all Perl code and stuff
  related to running the web application and "replayd" daemon that
  does the actual work related to requests made by the user; also
  contains the code used to do the nowification and a tool called
  "nowify" that can be run at the commandline

DESCRIPTION
- this file

QUICK-START
- some basic information on setting this thing up again
